  "description": "Gap Fill Mean Reversion sur SPY daily. Fade les gaps techniques (1-3%) sans catalyst institutionnel (volume faible). Les gaps sans catalyst se remplissent a 70%+ historiquement. Position inverse du gap.",
  "asset": "SPY",
  "timeframe": "1D",
  "parameters": {
